sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant W as Browser<br/>(web-app)
    participant API as Identity Core API<br/>(api.fivucsas.com)
    participant BIO as Biometric Service<br/>(internal-only)

    U->>W: start face enrollment
    W->>W: getUserMedia capture --<br/>MediaPipe FaceLandmarker (478 pts)
    note right of W: client pre-gate (advisory):<br/>face present, passive-liveness 0.45,<br/>quality hint, crop to 224 x 224 JPEG

    W->>API: POST /api/v1/biometric/enroll/userId<br/>multipart image, Bearer JWT,<br/>X-Request-Nonce header
    API->>API: edge + filter gates: Traefik TLS,<br/>rate limit, anti-replay nonce<br/>(Redis, 5-min TTL), JWT auth,<br/>RBAC biometric:enroll or self,<br/>tenant scope

    API->>BIO: POST /api/v1/enroll<br/>X-API-Key, Docker network only<br/>(optional Idempotency-Key)
    BIO->>BIO: image validation:<br/>content type + magic bytes

    BIO->>BIO: passive liveness -- MiniFASNet<br/>(UniFace backend, shared ONNX session)

    alt frame not live
        BIO-->>API: 400 LIVENESS_FAILED {score}
        API-->>W: enrollment rejected
        W-->>U: retry with a live capture
    else frame is live
        BIO->>BIO: anti-spoof assembler (13 analyzers)<br/>+ single-frame EAR veto<br/>(avg EAR below 0.18 = closed eyes)
        alt spoof verdict
            BIO-->>API: 403 ANTISPOOF_BLOCKED {reason}
            API-->>W: enrollment rejected
            W-->>U: blocked: spoof suspected
        else clean frame
            note over BIO: continues in part (b):<br/>detect, quality gate, embed, store
        end
    end
